divs: Sighting Detailsnoticed a light rotating in the sky when out for a walk, had Binocs and seen a disc with rotating lights. it was c;ose to the horizon lower that a planet, while the stars went through its rotation it stayed in the same spot when i started talking to it , gone in a blink. It dimed down and got bright and zipped off toward the east. it was sittiing in the northern sky above route 23. It has been showing up in differnt segments of the sky since then.
